name: Set of 5 Love-A-Bull Lacquer Polishes
description:
This is the full set of the five original polishes. Set includes:
Sea Breeze, a teal/blue base filled with small blue holo glitter (top left image)
Enduring Sunflower, a lovely bright yellow that dries matte (bottom left image)
Plum Crazy, a purple base filled with small purple holo glitter (top right image)
Grass Stains, a sheer green base with matte green glitter (bottom right image) 
Summer Nights, a blue black with gunmetal hex glitter (center image)

All polishes are 3 free and animal friendly!

**This price includes shipping!**

Image credit to IG @madamluck
